sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant CA as Credential<br/>Authority
    participant V as Verifier
    note over W, V: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>W: Generate Credential Key Pair
    W->>W: Create Evidence (Quote)<br/> including Credential Key Pop
    W->>W: Create Credential Request<br/>incl. Evidence and Credential Key PoP
    W->>CA: Request Credential<br/>passing Credential Request
    CA->>V: Forward Evidence<br/>from Credential Request
    V->>V: Appraise Evidence
    V->>V: Compute<br/>Attestation Results<br/>from Evidence
    V->>CA: Attestation<br/>Results
    CA->>CA: Compute Credential Attributes<br/>from Attestation Results
    CA->>CA: Create and Sign Credential<br/>from Credential Request<br/>and Credential Attributes
    CA->>W: Credential
